data.description: **Turnkey Beachside Retreat in Panama City Beach!** Step into a sun-drenched haven, thoughtfully furnished and ready for you. Its open-concept design showcases soaring cathedral ceilings, complemented by easy-care tile floors and plush carpeting in its two spacious bedrooms. Relish in the modern touch of brand new stainless steel appliances. For added convenience, an exterior storage space neatly tucks away any extras, while the expansive parking caters effortlessly to boats, RVs, and trailers. With septic taken care of in the front yard, the backyard is an open canvas for a pool! Immerse yourself in the best of coastal living, with the iconic sugar-white sands of the Gulf of Mexico just four blocks away. Outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the proximity to a public boat ramp with deep water access to bring your boat or kayaks. Indulge in local dining gems, and never miss a sunset with beach accesses at your doorstep all within walking distance. Rick Seltzer Park and St. Andrews State Park offer nearby escapes for picnics and nature appreciation. A/C replaced (2021) and a new well pump (2023). Your beachside sanctuary awaits!
